\c 11
\nb
\v 1 URehobhowamu esefikile eJerusalema wabuthanisa indlu yakoJuda leyakoBhenjamini, abakhethiweyo abazinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili, abalwa impi, ukuze balwe loIsrayeli ukubuyisela umbuso kuRehobhowamu.
\v 2 Kodwa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuShemaya umuntu kaNkulunkulu lisithi:
\v 3 Khuluma kuRehobhowamu indodana kaSolomoni, inkosi yakoJuda, lakuIsrayeli wonke koJuda lakoBhenjamini\x + 1 Kho. 12.23.\x*, uthi:
\v 4 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Kaliyikwenyuka njalo lingalwi labafowenu. Buyelani ngulowo endlini yakhe, ngoba linto yenziwe yimi. Basebelilalela ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, baphenduka ekuyenimelana loJerobhowamu\x + 28.8.\x*.
\s Ukuphumelela kukaRehobhowamu
\p
\v 5 URehobhowamu wasehlala eJerusalema, wakha imizi eyizinqaba koJuda\x + 11.10,23. 8.5. 12.4. 14.6. 17.2,19. 21. 3.\x*.
\v 6 Wasesakha iBhethelehema\x + Gen. 35.19.\x* leEtamu\x + Hlu. 15.8. 1 Lan. 4.3,32.\x* leThekhowa\x + 2 Sam. 14.2.\x*
\v 7 leBeti-Zuri\x + Josh. 15.58. Neh. 3.16. 1 Lan. 2.45.\x* leSoko\x + Josh. 15.35. 1 Kho. 4.10.\x* leAdulamu\x + 1 Sam. 22.1.\x*
\v 8 leGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x* leMaresha\x + 20.37. Josh. 15.44.\x* leZifi\x + Josh. 15.24.\x*
\v 9 leAdorayimi leLakishi\x + Josh. 10.3.\x* leAzeka\x + Josh. 10.10.\x*
\v 10 leZora\x + Josh. 15.33.\x* leAjaloni\x + Josh. 10.12.\x* leHebroni\x + Josh. 10.3.\x*, eyayikoJuda lakoBhenjamini, imizi ebiyelweyo.
\v 11 Waseqinisa izinqaba, wabeka abalawulimabutho kizo, leziphala zokudla lamafutha lewayini.
\v 12 Lakuwo wonke umuzi lomuzi \add wabeka\add* izihlangu ezinkulu lemikhonto, wayiqinisa kakhulukazi. Njalo uJuda loBhenjamini babengabakhe.
\p
\v 13 Labapristi lamaLevi ababekoIsrayeli wonke bazimisa kuye bevela kuyo yonke imingcele yabo.
\v 14 Ngoba amaLevi atshiya amadlelo awo lemfuyo yabo, aya koJuda leJerusalema\x + Nani 35.2.\x*, ngoba uJerobhowamu lamadodana akhe bawala ekusebenzeleni iN\nd kosi\nd* njengabapristi\x + 13.9.\x*;
\v 15 wasezibekela abapristi bendawo eziphakemeyo\x + 1 Kho. 12.31.\x*, labamadimoni\x + Levi 17.7.\x*, labamathole ayewenzile\x + 1 Kho. 12.28.\x*.
\v 16 Lemva kwawo kweza eJerusalema labo ababenikele inhliziyo yabo ukuyidinga iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, bevela kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli, ukuyahlabela iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + 15.9. 16.1. 30.11,18.\x*.
\v 17 Ngokunjalo bawuqinisa umbuso wakoJuda, benza uRehobhowamu indodana kaSolomoni waba lamandla iminyaka emithathu; ngoba bahamba endleleni kaDavida loSolomoni iminyaka emithathu\x + 12.1.\x*.
\p
\v 18 URehobhowamu wasezithathela uMahalathi indodakazi kaJerimothi indodana kaDavida waba ngumka\add khe\add*, \add lo\add*Abihayili indodakazi kaEliyabi indodana kaJese\x + 1 Sam. 16.6. 17.13,28. 1 Lan. 2.13.\x*,
\v 19 owamzalela amadodana, oJewushi loShemariya loZahamu.
\v 20 Langemva kwakhe wathatha uMahaka\x + 13.2. 1 Kho. 15.2.\x* indodakazi kaAbisalomu\x + 2 Sam. 14.27.\x*, owamzalela oAbhiya\x + 1 Kho. 14.31.\x* loAthayi loZiza loShelomithi.
\v 21 URehobhowamu wasemthanda uMahaka indodakazi kaAbisalomu okwedlula bonke omkakhe labafazi bakhe abancinyane - ngoba wathatha abafazi abalitshumi lesificaminwembili, labafazi abancinyane abangamatshumi ayisithupha, wazala amadodana angamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili lamadodakazi angamatshumi ayisithupha.
\v 22 URehobhowamu\x + Dute. 21.15-17.\x* wasebeka uAbhiya indodana kaMahaka waba yinhloko ukubusa phakathi kwabafowabo, ngoba kwakuyikumenza inkosi\x + 1 Kho. 14.31.\x*.
\v 23 Wenza ngokuhlakanipha, wasabalalisa kuwo wonke amadodana akhe emazweni wonke akoJuda lakoBhenjamini, kuwo wonke umuzi obiyelweyo, wawanika ukudla ngobunengi\x + Gen. 45.23.\x*, wadinga inengi labafazi\x + Dute. 14.26.\x*.